ay dapat na matindi.

00:36:44.520 --> 00:36:45.940
Marahil ay hindi kita dapat himukin
na isulat muli,

00:36:47.590 --> 00:36:48.690
pero habang iniisip ko,

00:36:50.230 --> 00:36:51.170
mas alam kong may isang bagay

00:36:52.440 --> 00:36:53.460
may gusto pa akong sabihin sayo.

00:36:53.480 --> 00:36:55.570
Kami ay upang makakuha mula dito hanggang doon.

00:36:56.230 --> 00:36:57.570
Noon, sa isang twist ng kapalaran,

00:36:58.750 --> 00:36:59.980
